IMC Global elects Fowler as CEO . IMC Global Inc said Thursday its board elected Robert Fowler Jr to succeed Wendell Bueche as chief executive officer of the company , effective July 1 , 1997 . Bueche will continue as chairman of the board . Fowler joined the company as president and chief operating officer and a director upon completion of the merger between IMC Global and Vigoro Corp on March 1 , 1996 . Prior to the merger , he was Vigoro ' s president and chief executive officer . IMC Global markets crop nutrients , including nitrogen , and related products . It also sells potash and other products to industrial users and produces sulphur and oil through joint ventures . ( ( - - Chicago newsdesk 312 408 - 8787 ) ) 
